&lt;li&gt;Manage data mapping, transformation, and validation processes across inbound and outbound integrations ensuring accuracy, consistency, and compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee integration lifecycle management, code migration, and production hyper care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted advisor on Workday integration best practices and design patterns, collaborating with HR, IT, and business stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare for and lead activities around Workday releases, including impact analysis, regression testing, and adoption of new integration or Extend features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, test, and deploy integration business processes, calculated fields, condition rules, and data transformations to support operational workflows&lt;/li&gt;
